      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, offering a showroom-quality aesthetic and flawless mechanical integrity. Discerning collectors will appreciate the immaculate cabin and the preservation of its original factory luster. An investment-grade opportunity for those who demand nothing less than automotive perfection.",
