      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I'm parting with this absolute beauty, and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure every inch stays spotless. It drives like a total dream and is just waiting for someone who will appreciate its pristine condition. Come take it for a spin, you seriously won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade E46 M3 in concours condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 power plant, exhibiting perfect compression across all six cylinders with recent valve clearance adjustments. The rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with plates, and the VANOS system has been overhauled using uprated seals and a machined oil pump disk. Power is transmitted via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring factory-spec kinematics. With no evidence of thermal cycling fatigue on the headers and a pristine undercarriage, this is a mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
